title: Experience Hendrix- The Best of Jimi Hendrix
description: Haven't uploaded before so I'm really just testing this out. All songs are at 320kbps. The genre might not make some of you happy. I generalize my genres so there aren't 400 different listings under "genre" (metal, speed metal, black metal, death metal, thrash metal - retarded. It's just "metal".) so I can hit play and get a bit of a mix of different eras.
